  "texts": [
    "However, we use only 12 relations, since we wanted to reserve some relations for outof-distribution test set.",
    "To avoid cherry-picking, the 12 relations used in our train, development and test sets are randomly sampled.",
    "The resulting relations are presented in Tables 4 and 5.",
    "We reserved the remaining 12 relations for outof-distribution test set.",
    "However, we found that in those 12 reserved relations, 5 were too similar to some of the relations that we train on (Table 4), thus we suspected that this could lead to a test set that is not truly out-of-distribution."
